latestIgtvVideos.title: Tequila Cider
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This cocktail recipe from @jaylynn_little has us excited for 5 o’clock to arrive! We can’t wait to try this recipe.

Tequila Cider:
1oz Tequila
3oz Apple Cider
4 dashes Angostura bitters
2 cinnamon sticks
Hard cider

Fill a shaker with ice and add the tequila, apple cider, bitters, and one cinnamon stick, then shake well. Pour over ice and top with your favorite hard cider. Garnish with fresh cranberries and a cinnamon stick.
